    <briefdescription>
<para>Battery manager class derived from task base class. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><hruler/>
</para>
<para><simplesect kind="par"><title>Detailed Description </title><para>The Battery manager task received report requests from power manager, which trigger an ADC request from battery manager to AD converter task. The measured values will than received from AD converter task, which send them to data manager task. There they will be added to metrics JSON string. See also <ref refid="_m_s_c_1SubSectionMetricsTx" kindref="member">Message Sequence Chart Cyclic Metrics</ref>. <linebreak/>
 The AD converter class provides methods specify the ADC channels used for battery management, to retrieve the specified ADC channels and to request an report with measured values from AD converter task. <bold>Message Interaction:</bold><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Receive<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Power manager task</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Transmit<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>AD converter task</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Data manager task </para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</simplesect>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
